values: Tara Reade says Joe Biden sexually assaulted her in 1993.  After talking publicly about it, she says she's so fearful for her well-being that she left the country and moved to Moscow.

Former Senate aide Tara Reade credibly accused Joe Biden of sexual assault. Now the DoJ is after her and she’s moved to Russia seeking political asylum. We spoke to her in Moscow.
